data.description: Gorgeous two story home on a large corner lot in the desirable community of Teravista. This spacious floorplan features four bedrooms, two and a half bathrooms, a formal dining room, a 2-story living room, and a game room upstairs! When entering, high ceilings and a beautiful foyer greet you. The gourmet kitchen has impressive features like granite countertops, a breakfast bar and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. The kitchen overlooks the spacious living room with floor-to-ceiling windows and a gas log fireplace. The primary bedroom is on the main floor with a bonus closet under the stairs perfect for extra storage. The primary bedroom has both a jetted tub and separate shower, double vanities and large walk-in closet. Walk upstairs into a spacious game room / second living area with storage closet right outside. All secondary bedrooms are up with one next to the game room and the two others across the breezeway. Head to the backyard to entertain friends and family on this extended patio and private backyard! Teravista is home to an 18-hole public golf course, two tennis courts, a basketball court, a pickleball court, two fitness centers, and three pools. Playscapes, parks and walking/jogging trails are scattered throughout the community encouraging a healthy, fun, and relaxed outdoor lifestyle. Located minutes from shopping, medical, IH-35, and so much more!
